      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so when you mention a \"lack of cultural and economic sophistication\" in these non-western groups, are you saying that these societies are actually behind in their development? like, is there an objective way to say one culture is more sophisticated than another, or is it all just based on what the west thinks?",
